## Rules for this mission

- **No drilling ahead.** Each slice gets its own ~30-min rock drill when you reach it. Do not pre-design slices 2+.
- **Each slice is shippable on its own.** Slice 1 ships as a feature-flagged endpoint with hard-coded behavior. Slice 2 makes it correct for one set of cases. Etc.
- **Acceptance tests grow by addition, not mutation.** Each slice adds new acceptance tests. The walking skeleton's test stays green forever.

